{"tid":1695280,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"巴黎展出抗爭運動為題的畫作及影片，需要眾籌!","createTime":"2019-11-05T14:13:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T04:05:48.000Z","uid":89679,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"9d2ef5866b6035394ca662de9945c60317ec9cf6","tid":1695280,"uid":89679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T14:13:21.000Z","msg":"(手動轉)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/hong-kong-water-and-ashes-arts-exhibition-in-paris-dec19/?fbclid=IwAR2HNw6lpdH2YePcsLeu-KdzYDLUtf-u_7VqjmWLIV0qc-2uQp6nVEy8gd4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fhong-kong-water-and-ashes-arts-exhibition-in-paris-dec19%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2HNw6lpdH2YePcsLeu-KdzYDLUtf-u_7VqjmWLIV0qc-2uQp6nVEy8gd4&d=YDk3w6YkG5F4GHIJWz3fGDsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=fa3462ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/hong-kong-water-and-ashes-arts-exhibition-in-paris-dec19/?fbclid=IwAR2HNw6lpdH2YePcsLeu-KdzYDLUtf-u_7VqjmWLIV0qc-2uQp6nVEy8gd4</a><br />\n本年12月3至7日, 我們將於巴黎舉辦為期5天的室內展覽,<br />\n展出以香港這場抗爭運動為題的畫作及影片，參展的作品主要來自香港藝術家, 藝術家用他們作品反映時代、回應時代。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pRF9hFw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpRF9hFw.jpg&h=935344ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XpmDVsc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXpmDVsc.jpg&h=0834b43b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nG3nCFx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnG3nCFx.jpg&h=14a3ec43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4sjJ6yS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4sjJ6yS.jpg&h=f43cd9eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我們希望透過此展覽，讓更多人，特別是法國的政界和文化藝術界人士，認知香港目前的嚴峻情況，<br />\n包括但不限於政府縱容警察暴力、執法不公、侵犯人權，以及打壓集會及新聞自由。<br />\n法國人熱愛文化藝術活動，這次藝術展，可以讓大眾從新聞報導以外的角度認識及探討香港的抗爭運動，透過視覺的感官體會，讓參加者可以確切理解香港人正在面對的困境。<br />\n此外，我們亦會邀請歐洲議會議員、法國政治領袖及資深大學學者，為此展覽發表錄像或演講，以展示海外人士對香港的支持。<br />\n我們已經訂好場地及準備了各類展品，現正急需經費支持以下項目:<br />\n<br />\n(1) 展品的印刷或可視化(約1,200歐元)<br />\n(2) 展覽場地佈置的開支(約1,300歐元)<br />\n(3) 邀請嘉賓的行政成本(約700歐元)<br />\n(4) 展覽宣傳及物流的開支 (約1,800歐元)<br />\n我們由衷希望閣下能捐款支持此展覽。<br />\n<br />\n我們要讓香港抗爭藝術衝出國際! 爭取國際社會的關注及支持!<br />\n<br />\n部分參展的藝術家名單如下(排名不分先後):<br />\n黃國才（香港）<br />\n黃照達（香港）<br />\n巴丟草（澳洲）<br />\n陳世樂（香港）<br />\n盧樂謙（香港）<br />\n何博欣（香港）<br />\nNicola Longobardi（香港）<br />\nHarcourt Romanticist（香港）<br />\nDiana Wege（美國）<br />\n<br />\n捐款連結<br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/hong-kong-water-and-ashes-arts-exhibition-in-paris-dec19/?fbclid=IwAR2HNw6lpdH2YePcsLeu-KdzYDLUtf-u_7VqjmWLIV0qc-2uQp6nVEy8gd4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fhong-kong-water-and-ashes-arts-exhibition-in-paris-dec19%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2HNw6lpdH2YePcsLeu-KdzYDLUtf-u_7VqjmWLIV0qc-2uQp6nVEy8gd4&d=YDk3w6YkG5F4GHIJWz3fGDsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=fa3462ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/hong-kong-water-and-ashes-arts-exhibition-in-paris-dec19/?fbclid=IwAR2HNw6lpdH2YePcsLeu-KdzYDLUtf-u_7VqjmWLIV0qc-2uQp6nVEy8gd4</a>"},{"pid":"df1c4fafded64971e523f686577ed792df8cb4a7","tid":1695280,"uid":288360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T15:03:16.000Z","msg":"Fai di push la, non-p ba da"},{"pid":"5324821d33f41acd8d0310914f4a6e56ffe2bd60","tid":1695280,"uid":117252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T06:15:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9c797782a049d1d548a5611f2a4216dce4e5039a","tid":1695280,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T14:29:34.000Z","msg":"捐左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01c1b3adce063766a88335c0d579c6675a2c8e87","tid":1695280,"uid":86113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T15:46:27.000Z","msg":"捐左"},{"pid":"a6974477cd7d8a867dd96c4f217c44a39d495614","tid":1695280,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,